Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.96,0:00:08.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的伊奧利亞·修亨伯格的亡靈們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.05,0:00:11.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我亞歷桑德羅·柯納
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.56,0:00:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要將你們作為通往新世界的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.44,0:00:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.90,0:00:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.46,0:00:34.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia  刹那·F·清榮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.17,0:00:36.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅逐目標！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.96,0:00:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  瞄準貨櫃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運氣好的話  至少能把那兩隻手臂炸飛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.49,0:00:47.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.73,0:00:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.75,0:00:55.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.51,0:00:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  沒損傷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.48,0:01:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度就想和Alvatore對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.07,0:01:06.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.48,0:02:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特  彙報Meister們的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nadleeh被重創
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特瑞亞沒有回話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:50.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios  機體損傷甚大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.49,0:02:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與2台敵MS交戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.54,0:02:56.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:03:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長翅膀的躲在衛星裡的某處
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:03.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種機體狀況不可能逃得太遠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:07.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  失策了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:09.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.28,0:03:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別拉我後腿  阿里路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在生死關頭什麼都做不了的你沒什麼用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:14.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子會活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是踏著他人的鮮血也要活下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.87,0:03:23.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒有聽到世界的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:25.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連戰鬥的意義也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在知道這些以前  我不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.29,0:03:34.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  終於有這種想法了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:39.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就讓那個女的見識一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的「超兵」是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直擊路線
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.81,0:03:49.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我躲給你看！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:54.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配合軸線
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.44,0:03:55.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.27,0:03:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:03:59.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.90,0:04:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台機體為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:17.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直和之前一樣可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣吧  哈里路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.39,0:04:43.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種武器和Throne的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.29,0:04:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  對接
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.06,0:04:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Armor嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.02,0:05:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fang
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Field展開
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄準狙擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.44,0:05:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯啊  躲開了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.89,0:05:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.19,0:05:54.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝過去了哦  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.15,0:05:56.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢到不可救藥了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:04.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.77,0:06:07.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:18.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完呢！  再來一擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.81,0:06:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  要記住我們的存在…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.23,0:06:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.77,0:07:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.75,0:07:17.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就1台Gundam就把我的Alvatore…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:30.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:46.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.62,0:07:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該是完美的超兵的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不知道啊  女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:54.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才不是什麼完美的超兵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是靠腦量子波得到了超反射能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.57,0:08:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你在這個速度範圍內的思考跟不上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:05.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是像動物一樣按本能行動而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以動作被我看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.48,0:08:13.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,融合反射與思考…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.89,0:08:17.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是超兵應有的姿態！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.63,0:08:21.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那光芒是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:22.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.70,0:08:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:24.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:39.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永別了  女人！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:45.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩麗絲！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:08:59.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校  中校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:10.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什麼  別管我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去戰鬥  少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:13.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.91,0:09:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果中校不在了  我就會成一個人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:36.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪  瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  為什麼你會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.04,0:09:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞  快回答  拉塞！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.66,0:09:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.92,0:10:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是擁有原版太陽爐的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不成熟的駕駛員竟然能讓我這麼痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.49,0:10:17.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把伊奧利亞的計劃歪曲的人  是你嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟計劃一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:22.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過主角變成我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:27.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  主角是我亞歷桑德羅·柯納！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想要什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞和再生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:34.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由Celestial Being的武力介入  世界滅亡和統一的再生開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我將把世界染上我的顏色！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想支配世界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.64,0:10:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是導上正軌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這個新世界沒有你的容身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:10:59.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化為粉末吧  Exia！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜啊  伊奧利亞·修亨伯格
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,統合世界  把人類帶向新的時代的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.85,0:11:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在仍存活的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.87,0:11:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什  什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:41.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個是！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.75,0:11:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞的系統嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.59,0:11:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.94,0:11:49.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到世界的扭曲了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.28,0:11:52.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  你就是元兇！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再生已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.63,0:12:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要繼續破壞嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Field…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.39,0:12:19.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  知道為什麼Exia會裝備實體劍嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:22.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了對抗GN Field
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.19,0:12:26.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計劃裡面也有對Gundam的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.27,0:12:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候你就是王牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就看你的了  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  洛克恩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.89,0:12:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是只會戰鬥的破壞者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會戰鬥  為了打倒引發爭鬥的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將這扭曲破壞！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:56.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以武力根除戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:01.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Field被…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam將達成此願！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:08.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:11.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我…！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:17.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.85,0:13:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李  李本茲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞歷桑德羅·柯納
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:29.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你表演了一出很不錯的滑稽劇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:30.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.05,0:13:33.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是伊奧利亞·修亨伯格的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:36.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而成了我的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李  李本茲  你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,統一後世界的前進方向就交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.79,0:13:46.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙…把柯納一族的夙願給…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.19,0:13:50.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為說這些  您才顯得氣量狹隘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李本茲！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:06.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flag？  裝配擬太陽爐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.98,0:14:18.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想死我了啊  Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.25,0:14:28.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光束軍刀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍華德和達利爾的仇  這次報定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.11,0:14:33.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用這GN Flag來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.82,0:14:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通訊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:43.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  那個時候的少年嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我和你是被命運的紅線綁在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是戰鬥的命運！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心被你壓倒性的性能奪走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:03.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種感覺  正是愛啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.28,0:15:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  愛超過了極致就變成了恨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.56,0:15:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像過激的信仰會引發內亂一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.31,0:15:17.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然知道的話  為什麼要戰鬥！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問軍人戰鬥的意義  是毫無意義的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:27.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被扭曲了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.98,0:15:30.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我變成這樣的是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.96,0:15:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名為Gundam的存在！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.85,0:15:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要打倒你！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:43.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界變成什麼樣都沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:45.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我自己的意識！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.99,0:15:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是世界的一部分嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.43,0:15:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這就是世界的聲音！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:56.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  你只不過是以自己的意志一意孤行而已！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.02,0:16:00.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的那種扭曲  就由我來切斷！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得好  Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.71,0:16:20.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍華德  達利爾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仇已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gun…Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.32,0:16:46.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能…在這裡結束…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.16,0:16:50.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計劃…仍然在繼續…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:56.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少…要把太陽爐…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.80,0:17:09.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nadleeh把GN Drive給…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:11.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特瑞亞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.08,0:17:15.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一來終於能安心去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:20.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能與你見面了…洛克恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.28,0:17:31.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…蘇摩·佩麗絲就是瑪麗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的嗎…哈里路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.21,0:17:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道的話  你就不會戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:39.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一死…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  反正結果都是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.81,0:17:49.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里路亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:06.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜·伊斯邁爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.74,0:18:10.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當你看到這訊息的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:12.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不在這個世上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.41,0:18:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以武力達到根除戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.23,0:18:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being讓只會戰鬥的我知道了戰鬥的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.61,0:18:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像那個時候的Gundam那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:31.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼世界如此的扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.86,0:18:39.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種扭曲來自何處
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:43.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼人有無意識的惡意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.83,0:18:47.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒有注意這種惡意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:52.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼有使人一生都為之癡狂的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.16,0:18:57.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼人會支配別人  被人支配
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:19:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要互相傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.63,0:19:02.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管這樣  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.65,0:19:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類還這樣生活著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在追求
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許等到遇見你的時候  就能回答這些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.79,0:19:20.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是以不同的道路追求同樣目標的你的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許能知曉人與人分別的道路…的答案…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.51,0:19:29.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.25,0:19:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在繼續追求
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Gundam一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Gundam…一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.05,0:19:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲  很久沒有給你發郵件了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.70,0:19:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自得到你的回答到現在已經過了2年了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.78,0:19:58.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有件事無論如何都想告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今年起就在宇宙工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.28,0:20:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然悲傷的事有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:11.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有一個小小的夢想終於達成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我想達成另一個夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你喲  路易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.02,0:20:21.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在宇宙等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.18,0:20:31.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是GN粒子的光吧？哪裡的機體？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.36,0:20:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個不是聯邦的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.34,0:20:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子的顏色不對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.85,0:20:42.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種光…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.62,0:20:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  那種光是…Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.35,0:21:00.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國際聯合改名為地球聯邦的第一年
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.45,0:21:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得到聯邦參加國全部328國的贊同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.02,0:21:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此宣佈將各國軍隊解體  統一為地球聯邦維和軍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.64,0:21:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值此所有國家的軍隊從此消失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.83,0:21:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們和平維持軍成為世界唯一的軍隊的時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界終於達成了真正的統一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.55,0:21:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將以此作為指引而奮力向前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.70,0:21:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣世界就能改變嗎  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.86,0:21:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.30,0:21:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的世界讓你滿意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.22,0:21:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很期待啊  世界能逐漸改變
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.29,0:21:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}　　　　　　　Innovator{\r}\N要開始了哦  改革者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.55,0:21:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.08,0:22:25.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑這麼遠辛苦了  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.36,0:22:27.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.18,0:22:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一台已經製造出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.99,0:22:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在做實戰的測試
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.91,0:22:33.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它機體呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.29,0:22:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟預定的一樣  預定按順序製造完成
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.68,0:22:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的話能不能讓我看看  第一世代的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.23,0:22:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.73,0:23:03.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是0 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.25,0:23:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一台搭載太陽爐並以其驅動的機體…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.89,0:23:11.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了太陽爐仍未安裝外  機體已經裝配完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.93,0:23:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這傢伙能適合的太陽爐也不好匹配
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.79,0:23:20.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是Exia的太陽爐  是否能順利尚且未知…
